小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvggZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=fb22b25f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvggZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=832b9928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvggZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=9ce53dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvggZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=9f2018c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cba107b8428e2d5eefbbcf9e6fed24874735922","tid":1746180,"uid":176991,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"之前去伊朗識到啲當地人，有互follow ig交流下，而家佢地全部都冇update，send message畀佢地全部冇回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8e5d938a637263f5d2e59bca9cb24ab4440bd3","tid":1746180,"uid":103363,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"6b3c3ebee519366d9af233f18cc79061201fc1ee","tid":1746180,"uid":40267,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:54:01.000Z","msg":"一個禮拜死成兩百個<img src=\